<urn:reckons:timeline/SPARQL10>
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#related> <urn:reckons:topic/SPARQL> ;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "First W3C Recommendation for querying RDF graphs. SPARQL is to triple stores what SQL is to relational databases. Enabled programmatic access to any RDF dataset." ;
    rdf:type <urn:kbase:type/Concept> ;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#related> <urn:reckons:timeline/LinkedDataPrinciples> ;
