    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#related> <urn:reckons:org/W3C> .

<urn:reckons:org/SchemaOrg>
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A collaborative vocabulary founded by Google, Bing, Yahoo, and Yandex in 2011. Provides structured data types for web content. Uses JSON-LD as the preferred format — the largest deployment of linked data on the web." ;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#related> <urn:reckons:org/W3C> ;
